{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0001", "text": "[Cybersecurity](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/veilig/index.html)", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0001", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 1, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 1}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0002", "text": "Many entrepreneurs wonder: Why do I need to check my suppliers? It may feel uncomfortable and may affect the collaboration. Yet the figures show why this is so important.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0002", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 2, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 2}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0003", "text": "Research by the Institute for Associations, Industries and Professions (IVBB) shows that most cyber attacks occur via suppliers and the supply chain:", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0003", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 3, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 3}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "1. Suppliers and supply chains – 40.1%\n2. Own technology with vulnerabilities – 35.8%\n3. Own employees (errors) – 24.1%", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0005", "text": "So many of the successful cyber attacks come through suppliers. That is why it is crucial to make clear agreements with them about cybersecurity.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0005", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 5, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 5}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0006", "text": "Some sectors are more attractive to cybercriminals than others. These are the top 10 sectors with the most cyber attacks:", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0006", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 6}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0007", "text": "1. Construction – 17%\n2. Manufacturing – 14%\n3. Healthcare – 14%\n4. Retail – 12%\n5. Technology – 11%\n6. Transport – 7%\n7.Legal – 7%\n8. Education – 6%\n9. Financial services – 6%\n10. Automotive – 6%\n11. Other sectors – 23%", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0007", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 7}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "Does your company fall on this list? Then it is extra important to arrange your cybersecurity properly and check your suppliers. They can be the weakest link.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "- Make clear agreements with suppliers about cybersecurity.\n- Check regularly whether they adhere to these agreements.\n- Assess risks and ensure backups and contingency plans.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "This article was produced in collaboration with [Samen Digitaal Veilig](https://samendigitaalveilig.nl/).", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0011", "text": "About 1 in 5 entrepreneurs is confronted with cybercrime. Such a cyber incident can have major consequences for business operations, customers, suppliers or reputation. Taking appropriate measures is therefore important for every company.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0011", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 11}}
{"id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0012", "text": "- Learn more about the 4-in-1 cyber solution [Cyber ​​Safe & Secure](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/cyber-veilig-en-zeker/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link) and reduce your cyber risks.\n- View smart tools, useful articles and cyber webinars on our [Safe entrepreneurship page](https://doorpassen.abnamro.nl/producten-en-diensten/veilig-ondernemen/?icmp=cm-od_article-insights_btn-link).\n- [Report fraud to us](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/prive/abnamro/veilig-banken/fraude-melden.html \"Report fraud\"), even if in doubt, after which our helpdesk will help you immediately.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers__a2-late-chunking__0012", "source_slug": "meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers", "source_title": "Most hacks originate through suppliers", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/cybersecurity/beveiliging/meeste-hacks-ontstaan-via-leveranciers.html", "source_date": "2025-05-12", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "beveiliging", "topic": "cybersecurity", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 12, "n_chunks_total": 15, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 12}}
